		<div class="mb-4">
			<span class="inline-block font-mono text-[0.625rem] tracking-widest uppercase text-[var(--site-text-muted)] bg-[var(--site-badge-bg)] border border-[var(--site-badge-border)] px-2 py-0.5 rounded mb-2">why this package</span>
